title: Investing, Building a following, and Bitcoin with Anthony Pompliano: Episode 14
description:
Will Clemente and Anthony Pompliano discuss investing, building a following, Bitcoin, and more for our weekly interview Podcast/YouTube channel series. Can now find our podcast on Spotify, Apple, and Google Podcasts as well! 


 Pomp's twitter: twitter.com/APompliano
